---
description: Respect existing code and patterns
globs: ["**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

This project already exists and already works visually.

Rules:
- respect existing naming
- respect existing component boundaries
- respect existing style patterns
- respect existing state patterns unless they are clearly broken
- respect current imports and aliases unless there is a real issue
- do not replace working code just because another style is preferred
- do not clean up by changing everything to your own format
- do not flatten or split components unless explicitly requested

When improving code:
- target the problem area only
- leave unrelated code alone
- preserve behavior
- preserve appearance
- preserve flow

Default behavior:
follow the app's existing conventions, not your own preferences.
